<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>관리자 로그인</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page narrow">
    <header class="sub-hero">
      <h1>관리자 로그인</h1>
      <p>관리자 전용 기능을 사용하려면 로그인하세요.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="top-actions">
      <a class="btn" href="/">목록으로</a>
    </div>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <p class="error-text"><%= error %></p>
    <% } %>

    <form method="post" action="/login" class="form-card">
      <label class="label">아이디</label>
      <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="관리자 아이디" required />

      <label class="label">비밀번호</label>
      <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호" required />

      <button type="submit" class="btn primary full">로그인</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
